<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q31_v5" title="Q31_v5" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En la información nutricional de un paquete de galletas de una nueva marca se indica que una porción de 4 galletas aporta <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi></m:math> kilocalorías en total.</p>
    <p>Para calcular cuántas kilocalorías <m:math><m:mi>K</m:mi></m:math> se ingieren al consumir este tipo de galletas se puede utilizar la fórmula
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>K</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>C</m:mi>
            <m:mo>⁢</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>,
      tal que <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> es la cantidad de galletas consumidas y <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi></m:math> es la cantidad de kilocalorías que aportan 4 galletas.</p>
    <p>Una persona consumió 6 galletas de este tipo junto a un vaso de jugo que contiene 60 kilocalorías, ingiriendo en total 360 kilocalorías.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuántas kilocalorías <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi></m:math> aportan 4 galletas de esta marca?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">200<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Del total de <m:math><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías, el jugo aporta <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:math>, así que las 6 galletas aportan <m:math><m:mn>360</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías. Entonces, 1 galleta aporta <m:math><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías y 4 galletas aportan <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>50</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        
        240
      <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn></m:math>, entonces 6 galletas aportarían <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías. Al sumar el jugo, el total sería <m:math><m:mn>360</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>420</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías, y no <m:math><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        
        280
      <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>280</m:mn></m:math>, entonces 6 galletas aportarían <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>280</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>420</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías. Al sumar el jugo, el total sería <m:math><m:mn>420</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>480</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías, y no <m:math><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        
        450
      <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>450</m:mn></m:math>, entonces 6 galletas aportarían <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>450</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>675</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías. Al sumar el jugo, el total sería <m:math><m:mn>675</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>735</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías, y no <m:math><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Determinar cuántas kilocalorías aportaron las galletas</strong></p>
            <p>La persona ingirió en total <m:math><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías y el jugo aporta <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías.</p>
            <p>Entonces, las 6 galletas aportaron:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>360</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Es decir, 6 galletas aportan <m:math><m:mn>300</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular cuántas kilocalorías aporta 1 galleta</strong></p>
            <p>Si 6 galletas aportan <m:math><m:mn>300</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías, entonces 1 galleta aporta:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, cada galleta aporta <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular cuántas kilocalorías aportan 4 galletas</strong></p>
            <p>Como cada galleta aporta <m:math><m:mn>50</m:mn></m:math> kilocalorías, 4 galletas aportan:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>50</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar con la fórmula dada</strong></p>
            <p>La fórmula es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>⁢</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
            <p>Si <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>200</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1&#160;200</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Estas son las kilocalorías de las 6 galletas. Al sumar el jugo:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>360</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Coincide exactamente con el total del enunciado.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La cantidad de kilocalorías que aportan 4 galletas es <m:math><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math>. La alternativa correcta es <strong>A</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>